# Trapping Exp: Biomass Data ====

# Manually fixed some errors in the csv file
TrapMort <- read.csv("Trapping_Alll_Data20Feb2018.csv")
# Only the buffer and WSM plants were harvested
TrapBio <- subset(TrapMort, Treat != "Soil")

# Shoot Data
